,19,0z\"\/><\/g><\/svg><\/span> <span class=\"wprm-recipe-details-label wprm-block-text-uppercase wprm-recipe-servings-label\">Makes <\/span><span class=\"wprm-recipe-servings wprm-recipe-details wprm-recipe-servings-2138 wprm-recipe-servings-adjustable-tooltip wprm-block-text-uppercase\" data-initial-servings=\"\" data-recipe=\"2138\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\">6<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wprm-recipe-meta-container wprm-recipe-times-container wprm-recipe-details-container wprm-recipe-details-container-separate wprm-block-text-uppercase\"><div class=\"wprm-recipe-block-container wprm-recipe-block-container-separate wprm-block-text-uppercase wprm-recipe-time-container wprm-recipe-prep-time-container\" style=\"\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-details-label wprm-block-text-bold wprm-recipe-time-label wprm-recipe-prep-time-label\">Prep Time <\/span><span class=\"wprm-recipe-time wprm-block-text-uppercase\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-details wprm-recipe-details-minutes wprm-recipe-prep_time wprm-recipe-prep_time-minutes\">15<span class=\"sr-only screen-reader-text wprm-screen-reader-text\"> minutes<\/span><\/span> <span class=\"wprm-recipe-details-unit wprm-recipe-details-minutes wprm-recipe-prep_time-unit wprm-recipe-prep_timeunit-minutes\" aria-hidden=\"true\">mins<\/span><\/span><\/div><div class=\"wprm-recipe-block-container wprm-recipe-block-container-separate wprm-block-text-uppercase wprm-recipe-time-container wprm-recipe-cook-time-container\" style=\"\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-details-label wprm-block-text-bold wprm-recipe-time-label wprm-recipe-cook-time-label\">Cook Time <\/span><span class=\"wprm-recipe-time wprm-block-text-uppercase\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-details wprm-recipe-details-minutes wprm-recipe-cook_time wprm-recipe-cook_time-minutes\">10<span class=\"sr-only screen-reader-text wprm-screen-reader-text\"> minutes<\/span><\/span> <span class=\"wprm-recipe-details-unit wprm-recipe-details-minutes wprm-recipe-cook_time-unit wprm-recipe-cook_timeunit-minutes\" aria-hidden=\"true\">mins<\/span><\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wprm-spacer\" style=\"height: 30px;\"><\/div>\n<div id=\"recipe-2138-ingredients\" class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredients-container wprm-recipe-ingredients-no-images wprm-recipe-2138-ingredients-container wprm-block-text-normal wprm-ingredient-style-regular wprm-recipe-images-before\" data-recipe=\"2138\" data-servings=\"6\"><h3 class=\"wprm-recipe-header wprm-recipe-ingredients-header wprm-block-text-uppercase wprm-align-left wprm-header-decoration-none\" style=\"\">Ingredients<\/h3><div class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-group\"><ul class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredients\"><li class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" data-uid=\"0\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-amount\">1<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-name\"><a href=\"https:\/\/toscanoauthentic.com.au\/product\/traditional-waffles-copy\/\" class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-link\">pack <u><strong>Toscano Frozen Petite Liege Style Waffles<\/strong><\/u><\/a><\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-notes wprm-recipe-ingredient-notes-faded\">(6 waffles)<\/span><\/li><li class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" data-uid=\"1\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-amount\">1<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-unit\">cup<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-name\">250g thick Greek-style yogurt or cream<\/span><\/li><\/ul><\/div><div class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-group\"><h5 class=\"wprm-recipe-group-name wprm-recipe-ingredient-group-name wprm-block-text-uppercase\">Blueberry topping<\/h5><ul class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredients\"><li class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" data-uid=\"3\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-amount\">250<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-unit\">g<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-name\">fresh or frozen blueberries<\/span><\/li><li class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" data-uid=\"4\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-amount\">1\/3<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-unit\">cup<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-name\">80ml freshly squeezed orange juice<\/span><\/li><li class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" data-uid=\"5\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-amount\">2<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-unit\">tablespoons<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-name\">caster sugar<\/span><\/li><\/ul><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"wprm-layout-column wprm-column-width-50\">\n\n\t\t\n\n<div id=\"recipe-2138-instructions\" class=\"wprm-recipe-instructions-container wprm-recipe-2138-instructions-container wprm-block-text-normal\" data-recipe=\"2138\"><h3 class=\"wprm-recipe-header wprm-recipe-instructions-header wprm-block-text-uppercase wprm-align-left wprm-header-decoration-none\" style=\"\">Instructions<\/h3><div class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction-group\"><ul class=\"wprm-recipe-instructions\"><li id=\"wprm-recipe-2138-step-0-0\" class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><div class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">To make the blueberry topping, combine the blueberries, orange juice and sugar in a small saucepan over medium heat and stir until the sugar is dissolved. Reduce the heat and simmer for 5 minutes or until the berries start to collapse. Remove from the heat. Strain the berries and return the juice to the pan. Simmer for a further few minutes until syrupy. Return the blueberries and set aside to cool.<\/div><\/li><li id=\"wprm-recipe-2138-step-0-1\" class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><div class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"display: block;\">To warm your <a href=\"https:\/\/toscanoauthentic.com.au\/product\/traditional-waffles-copy\/\"><u><strong>Toscano Frozen Petite Liege Style Waffles<\/strong><\/u><\/a>, <\/span><div class=\"wprm-spacer\"><\/div><span style=\"display: block;\">a) preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C (200\u00b0C fan-forced). Place waffles on a baking tray. Bake for 4-6 minutes or until heated through. <\/span><div class=\"wprm-spacer\"><\/div><span style=\"display: block;\">b)\u00a0place in a toaster on the lowest setting and toast for 1-2 minutes or until heated through. <\/span><div class=\"wprm-spacer\"><\/div><span style=\"display: block;\">c)\u00a0preheat your air fryer to 180\u00b0C and heat waffles for 2 minutes or until heated through.<\/span><\/div><\/li><li id=\"wprm-recipe-2138-step-0-2\" class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><div class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"display: block;\">Remove and cool on a wire rack.<\/span><div class=\"wprm-spacer\"><\/div><span style=\"display: block;\"><strong>CAUTION: Crunchy sugar pieces may be hot after warming.<\/strong><\/span><\/div><\/li><li id=\"wprm-recipe-2138-step-0-3\" class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><div class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">Top warmed waffles with a swirl of yogurt or cream and a spoonful of berries and sauce. Serve immediately.<\/div><\/li><\/ul><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":2226,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"wprm-recipe-roundup-name":"","wprm-recipe-roundup-description":"","footnotes":""},"categories":[106,174],"tags":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-2152","1":"post","2":"type-post","3":"status-publish","4":"format-standard","5":"has-post-thumbnail","7":"category-all-recipes","8":"category-sweet"},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v27